<p><em><strong><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Course Complaint</span>&nbsp;</strong></em>- If you have an issue with a lesson in I-Learn, a broken link, typo, or anything<br />&nbsp;else of this nature, contact the&nbsp;<a href="http://www.byui.edu/online/online-support-center">Online Support Center</a>. &nbsp;</p>
<p><em><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>Instructor Communication Issue</strong></span>&nbsp;</em>- If it has been longer than 24 hours and your instructor<br />&nbsp;hasn't responded to your emails or phone calls, contact the&nbsp;<a href="http://www.byui.edu/online/online-support-center">Online Support Center</a>. &nbsp;&nbsp;</p>
<p><br /><em><strong>&nbsp;<span style="text-decoration: underline;">Instructor Complaint&nbsp;</span></strong></em>- If you feel you have been mistreated by your instructor, for example:&nbsp;<br />&nbsp;unfair grading, teacher wasn't helpful, offended etc. contact the&nbsp;<a href="http://www.byui.edu/online/online-support-center">Online Support Center</a>&nbsp;. &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<br /><br /><em>&nbsp;<span style="text-decoration: underline;"><em><strong>Grievance</strong></em><em><strong>&nbsp;-</strong></em></span></em>&nbsp;&nbsp;If your concern remains unresolved after you have tried all the other possible procedures above, you may want to file a grievance. &nbsp;A Grievance is a formal complaint against an &nbsp;instructor that will not remain anonymous and will ultimately result in some kind of action. &nbsp;In order to file a grievance, you must fill out the grievance form as completely as possible. &nbsp;Once your form has been sumitted, it will go to the Online Instruction department to be reviewed. &nbsp;They will be in contact with you to and will let you know what action is being taken in regards to your concern. &nbsp;If you have any questions about this process of would like more information before submitting a grievance, contact the Online Support Center. &nbsp;To file a grievance now, follow this link:&nbsp;<a href="https://byui.qualtrics.com/SE/?SID=SV_3qu751nAKU5bVvD">Grievance Form</a>.</p>
